text: Sepiddasht may refer to: * Sepiddasht Rural District, a rural district in Papi District, Khorramabad County, Lorestan Province, Iran * Sepiddasht, Lorestan, a city in and capital of Papi District, Khorramabad County, Lorestan Province, Iran * Sepiddasht, Alborz, a village in Fardis Rural District, in the Central District of Fardis County, Alborz Province, Iran
title: Sepiddasht
